        "content": "<p>alexcrichton opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13557\">PR #13557</a> from <code>alexcrichton:refactor-serve-debug</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>When debugging was integrated into <code>wasmtime serve</code> it effectively<br>\nduplicated the entire process of handling the TCP socket, accepting<br>\nconnections, dealing with Hyper, etc. This commit is targeted at<br>\nremoving all of this duplication and using the same path for<br>\ndebugging-and-not to ensure they don't diverge over time.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: this is bulit on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13555\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13555</a> currently </p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>",
